headline.main: Arnautovic Brace Sends Boro Into Bottom Three
headline.print_headline: Arnautovic Brace Sends Boro Into Bottom Three

lead_paragraph: Forward Marko Arnautovic's first-half double gave Stoke City a 2-0 win over Middlesbrough on Saturday and sent the visitors into the relegation zone for the first time this season.
